          <td colspan="2" valign="top" class="titulo2">New Chinese Poetry: The Origin and the Development
&#8212; From the Perspective of Cultural Exchanges between China and the West
 <span class="texto2">by <a href="../../issue10/zhimin-li/bio.php" class="link3">Zhimin Li</a>, a transcription of a presentation given at The  Kelly Writers House, University of Pennsylvania, Philadelphia, USA </span></td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
